<h2>Overview</h2>
  <li>Gather all lyrics for the record.</li>
  <li>Use iMovie to compile a music video for the record.</li>
  <li>Use GarageBand to record the vinyl and export the audio file.</li>
  <li>Use the lyrics, audio file and <a href="http://www.lrcgenerator.com/">LRC Generator</a> to create a <i>.lrc</i> file.</li>
  <li>Format the <i>.lrc</i> file as <i>.ass</i> to get a fading subtitles effect.</li>
  <li>Use <a href="https://ffmpeg.org/">FFmpeg</a> to add the subtitles to the music video file.</li>
